            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "聯茂營收表現佳 3月營收創新高 推升Q1營收91.43億元登頂",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_7onPlqV8SrRjkN2HHQ3AQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/eb41547dfc7270762a516c21b5191348\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E8%8C%82%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E4%BD%B3-3%E6%9C%88%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E9%AB%98-%E6%8E%A8%E5%8D%87q1%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B691-43%E5%84%84%E5%85%83%E7%99%BB%E9%A0%82-081253378.html",
